	heroSubhead={`The weight is real — the decisions that keep you up at night, the people depending on you, the pressure to produce results, the quiet loneliness of being the one everyone looks to. Here's the truth underneath the title: you have a Father in heaven who already delights in you, apart from anything you achieve or anyone you lead.`}
