	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you lead people, the Father's Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> These Bible verses for leaders meet you where the weight lives — the loneliness at the top, the decision fatigue, the imposter syndrome, the fear of letting everyone down. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on your phone — and it reveals God as a <em>Father</em> from beginning to end. Whether you searched "Bible verses for leaders," "scripture for business owners," or "godly leadership verses" — the answer starts in one place: you lead best from the security of being fathered first. You were a beloved son or daughter long before you led anyone, and servant leadership flows from received love.`}
	keyTakeaway={`You are not valuable because of your title, your team's results, or the weight you carry. You are the Father's beloved child right now — fathered first, leader second. Lead from the security of being loved, and serve from a love you've already received, not from one you're trying to earn.`}
	painsHeading={`The weight leaders carry`}
	painsIntroHtml={`If you feel isolated at the top, exhausted by the decisions, or like an imposter waiting to be found out, you are not weak and you are not alone. A whole generation of leaders carries the same weight — and the numbers say it out loud.`}
