	painsBodyHtml={`<p>Behind every statistic is a real leader — maybe you. The decision you keep turning over at 2 a.m. The people whose livelihoods ride on calls you have to make alone. The smile you hold in the meeting while running on empty. The quiet fear that one day everyone will discover you don't have it all figured out after all.</p><p>None of this means you're failing. It means you're human, carrying a load that was never meant to be carried alone — in a world that ties your worth to your output and your results. There is a Father who sees the real you underneath the title, and He has something to say about who you actually are.</p>`}
